Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you should have waited
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,until you're serialized to \Nmake a public announcement?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna tell the world, now's the best time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.32,0:00:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That way my fans will all vote for \Nme on those questionnaire thingies.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.97,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll succeed in a multitude of \Nmediums and become a true star.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.38,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing of his announcement is a cheap trick.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his fans'll definitely fill \Nout the questionnaire for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.95,0:00:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner of the "Golden Future Cup" would \Nbe in the best position for getting serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.75,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to get first, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.01,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.55,0:00:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's here then, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.93,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let Koogy get away with this.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.06,0:00:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How can they consent to something like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.56,0:00:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll teach the editing department a thing or two.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Fukuda,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,move out!
