Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.93,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have a seat in booth number one.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask what your business is today?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a visitor registration form, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. P—Please fill this in.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.83,0:02:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who here's got the most senior editor?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.56,0:03:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hm—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably Aoki's editor, Aida.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.92,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the team leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We could always go straight \Nto the chief editor, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.42,0:03:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to see Weekly Jack's Aida.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So he's asking for Aida—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's not available, then Hattori Akira.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he's not here either, then Hattori Yujiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Just a moment, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, this is Aida.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.06,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fukuda, Mr. Nakai, and \NMr. Ashirogi are here to see you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.65,0:03:44.11,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,All the entries for the "Golden Future Cup," huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.91,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This must be about the Koogy thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Send them up, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori! Yujiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got trouble on the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.47,0:03:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They've sure got some \Nnerve letting Koogy compete.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let the "Golden Future Cup" \Nturn into some lame popularity contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.02,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.51,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all pouring our souls into our manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.81,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You just wait, Jack editing department!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.21,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I'm sure you can guess why.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things are about to get noisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Evenin'!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to be young, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.54,0:04:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them isn't so young, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.70,0:04:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda, hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not here to talk to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let us talk to—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll talk to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is cheating, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Koogy, so he's going to have a few\N votes in the bag already then, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time he releases a new song,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.76,0:04:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,his CD sales and even online \Ndownloads hit top three in all the charts.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.43,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I absolutely don't want you to \Nlose to something like this "Colorfusical."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means Hattori knew this \Nwas going to happen, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.76,0:05:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's putting his music career \Non hiatus to draw manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's cheating at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.26,0:05:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think his fans will want him to \Nkeep writing music instead of drawing manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If his manga isn't any good, \Nhe's gonna be in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's prepared to take that risk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why is he making this announcement now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he just doing it to get \Nthe support of all his fans?
Comment: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He printed a comment asking for support
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.38,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it even says he's advertising \Nhimself on a bunch of music shows.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as a celebrity \Nrunning in an election, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the problem with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.77,0:05:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is the case, a manga \Nartist's job is based on his popularity.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.57,0:05:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the most popular person wins.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bullshit!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.35,0:05:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me you think it's \Nfair to do anything to get votes?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm a pacifist!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.09,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree with Fukuda!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't feel like we're competing \Nwith the content of our stories anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.34,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pouring everything I \Nhave into my manga this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my last chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already 33!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, then \Njust drop out of the contest!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.09,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The contest entries haven't been announced yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Koogy is the one you should \Nbe dropping from the contest!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.73,0:06:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already all over the news that he's \Nin the contest, so we can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying you'd be fine \Nwith all three of us dropping out?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still have the contest if that happens?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Fukuda, I don't really want to drop out.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing backing down now, Nakai?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.59,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just chicken out.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yeah, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.57,0:06:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There are plenty of other \Nentries we can choose from.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.19,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of newcomers are just \Nwaiting for their big chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.58,0:06:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just patronizing us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to take it that way, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that matters to us is \Nthat the readers enjoy our product.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga just needs to be interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is, then of course it'll be serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.54,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not dropping out.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is win, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just win with your story!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Manga just needs to be interesting.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is, then it'll be serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.40,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Koogy manages to win because \Nhis fans fill out the questionnaire,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be a false victory.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.32,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know if we win or lose \Nbased on the quality of our story.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.12,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that means we just have to write a story \Nthat won't lose to his and that'll be enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're just trying to sound cool,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.74,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battle of manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pound this Makaino Koji or \NKoogy or whoever into the ground!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's all check out each other's names.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all give each other feedback \Nto make our stories better.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that time with chapter five of "Crow."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't cheating.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be rivals, but we're \Nalso partners in this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.51,0:07:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori, can we get a copy of our name?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
