Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.50,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it alright if I bring Ashirogi back to your place to \Nhave a strategy meeting for the "Golden Future Cup?"
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.38,0:08:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-sensei? Of course they're welcome to come!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.27,0:08:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll see you soon, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.14,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all ended up deciding \Nto give each other feedback.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.80,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda, it's okay if Aoki comes too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.10,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that he would be delighted \Nif you would be so kind as to join us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I made enough copies for everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the readers will judge based on the story.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.80,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.64,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi, you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y—Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Fukuda, we're heading out.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.52,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to have caused a scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.07,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.34,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure are a bunch of troublemakers, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.50,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but if you don't have at least that much \Npassion, you can't become a popular mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've got that right.
