Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The news was true. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Koogy is still Koogy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.71,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.00,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is popular.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.74,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but still—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That Koogy bastard.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not taking manga seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm losing to him!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everybody.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Aoki is going to be a bit late.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, could you get some drinks and snacks ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And try and clean the room up a bit, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.31,0:09:41.84,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should take all the trash out, too—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.63,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai has totally lost sight of our goal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't some play date.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Things sure took a strange turn, didn't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.06,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We went in to talk about Koogy and \Nended up having a feedback meeting?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can make our story better by \Nsharing ideas, then it's fine with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they're all still our rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.53,NiizumaPlate,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,217.269)\fs66.852\c&HF0EBE6&\blur0.669}Niizuma
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.21,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma is busy working, so let's use this room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty messy, but just sit wherever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.76,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.29,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought our studio was pretty nice, \Nbut this place is pretty impressive too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time in this room, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.89,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangakas studios are all \Nbound to look similar, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let me help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you set out your names?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,P—Please, come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.55,0:10:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're coming in.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.80,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already met Ashirogi so I \Nguess that just leaves Fukuda, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.58,0:10:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Aoki Ko, the writer \Nof the story I'll be drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.99,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,He also works with me as an assistant for Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.93,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So this is the runner up for "Story King"—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.99,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'd heard she was a girl,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.99,0:10:51.58,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,And he's one of the participants in the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.83,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but just what kind of story is she writing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki, please have a seat.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and there are drinks as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.71,0:10:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for it being so cramped.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody settled in?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start by taking a look at each other's names.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My "Kiyoshi Knight."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai and Aoki's "Hideout Door."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.33,0:11:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ashirogi Muto's "Shady Detective Trap."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.94,0:11:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're finished reading all of \Nthem, we'll give our opinion on each.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold anything back.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Be straightforward and say whatever comes to mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get started.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like fun. May I join you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Niizuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Niizuma, what about your work?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.56,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure this will be a \Ngreat learning experience for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to help out!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.95,0:11:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha think?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like Niizuma to take a look at ours.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.79,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no objections.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm fine with it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's get \NNiizuma-sensei's opinion as well, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.75,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.62,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is the story I almost \Nended up drawing the art for.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.95,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of story it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.62,0:12:16.34,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is bad. Aoki Ko is better than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.34,0:12:18.59,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It almost feels like I'm \Nwatching a movie or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.05,0:12:23.18,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's just a story about a boy who meets a fairy and \Ndecides that he wants to become a fairy himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect the runner up \Nof "Story King" to be this good.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.02,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.90,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This story gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.78,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.78,0:12:40.15,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Although, it's something that isn't in Jack right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.19,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Are they considering that as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.19,0:12:45.57,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And I can't forget about Nakai's skill.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.37,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,If he can represent this world right—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.22,0:12:58.59,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Fukuda said he was going to redo his one-shot \Nthat came in seventh with the same characters,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.05,0:13:00.98,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,but this is almost completely different.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.98,0:13:04.47,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And we don't have anywhere \Nnear this level of humor.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.10,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This is really good.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.10,0:13:09.31,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It feels like a modern version of "Otokojyuku."
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.31,0:13:13.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,The action scenes are full of feeling and \Nthe comedy makes you laugh out loud.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.72,0:13:19.02,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I'd say his drawings are the worst here, \Nbut they fit well with the story's rough style.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.97,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,This story is way better than mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.97,0:13:35.42,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It looks like Mashiro was right when \Nhe said this guy could become a writer.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.92,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,So my real competition this \Ntime is Ashirogi Muto, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.41,0:13:42.79,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,I guess that calling these two "15 year \Nold geniuses" wasn't an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.79,0:13:46.24,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And it's not just the story, \Nthe art is outstanding, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.24,0:13:50.10,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's still just the name, but he's even \Ndrawing the characters in detailed poses.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.01,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,And the panel organization is great, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.01,0:13:55.29,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,When this is finished, it's \Ngoing to be really impressive.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And this guy over here—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Exciting!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, shall we move on to the critique?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.09,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.96,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And why exactly is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.95,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe my story is the best one here, \Nso doing so would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to continue, do so without me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You think this fluffy let's eat a giant chocolate cake
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in a house made of candy surrounded \Nby a field of flowers story is the best?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I thought it sucked!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. Mine is the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours is just full of filthy language.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because it's a shounen manga!!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.27,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll just take that as \Nyour critique then, shall I?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.23,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already been told to tone it \Ndown and redraw this six times.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep getting more and more \Nstrict about what you can write.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.62,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But even when I say that, they tell me not to \Ncompare things now with manga in the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's better to have more \Nshounen manga like this out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like they're textbooks \Nor some kind of holy book.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more interesting if parents are against it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,F—Fukuda, you don't have to be so—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.92,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my story was the best one here as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.13,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, you guys thought \Nyours was the best too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Overall, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess that means this critique is useless, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have faith in your own story, \Nthere is no need to continue.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I agree with Aoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.25,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And my manga will not lose to "Colorfusical."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.23,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.23,0:15:34.78,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,You mean our manga, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we stop here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.12,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like {\i1}Miss{\i0} Aoki here said.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have faith in your own story.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that everybody \Nthinks they're going to be first.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.88,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all agree that we don't \Nneed anybody else's opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.94,0:15:50.72,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.81,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,It's not just Koogy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.34,Default-Italic,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is a rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.04,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're already here, why don't \Nwe at least listen to Niizuma's opinion,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's the only neutral person here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.95,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I thought they were all fantastic.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.96,0:16:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But which one do you think was the most interesting?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Violence.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.68,0:16:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspense.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fairy-tale.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's stories are so different,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I were to put them in order \Nof which one I liked the most—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W—Wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda feel like if Niizuma-sensei \Nsays anything, then it'll come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident, so that's fine with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm confident as well
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can say it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.10,0:16:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.78,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided on who's third, but \Nthe other two are tied for first.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.74,0:16:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel kinda bad for the person in \Nthird, so I won't say any more than that.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A tie?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.99,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just pick one?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly believe that it is a tie for first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all you're going to say
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,then there was no point asking in the first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.64,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really is a tie.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.19,0:17:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we'll find out two months \Nfrom now when the results are announced.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the winner of the "Golden Future \NCup" be somebody sitting here?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will it be Koogy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.54,0:17:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.27,0:17:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.14,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Aoki, I'll walk you to the station.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.72,0:17:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, we should get going, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.94,0:17:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work everybody.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to reading the finished versions.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess there wasn't much point to all that, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.96,0:17:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody already thinks theirs is the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.55,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if you didn't, you wouldn't \Nbe trying to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You've been quiet since we left.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.01,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Which two stories were tied for first?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what's bothering you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda and Nakai's stories are both \Nbetter than I thought they would be.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we're not going to lose.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure of that yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just Eiji's personal opinion.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The real decision will be made by \Nthe questionnaire and a meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.69,0:18:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Koogy already has a huge \Nadvantage in the questionnaire.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.35,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And Koogy already got an honorable \Nmention in the Tezuka Award.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.76,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's giving up music just to write \Nmanga, we have no idea how it'll turn out.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no time left before the deadline.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can change a few things while \Nwe're doing the final manuscript.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.65,0:18:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the readers will judge based on the story.
