Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H9F6350&\fs33.426\pos(380,280.778)\blur1.003\frz9.5\fax-0.2}Performer's Dressing Room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.97,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H844E3F&\pos(513.333,474.648)\blur1.003\frz-0.2\fax-0.0}The Underclassmen
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.06,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.97,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is says that Koogy is going on hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad. I really liked him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.76,0:18:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, his announcement \Nyesterday sure was a surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he's going to be a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.76,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He claimed that his story is going to \Nrock the foundation of the manga world.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.03,0:19:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's going to be in \NShounen Jack's "Something-Cup,"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so he asked for everybody's support.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the "Golden Future Cup?"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the one.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.93,0:19:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a bit unfair, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a day after the announcement, \Nbut he already has all these fliers ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.02,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I like him so I'll support him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.55,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he gets an anime, \NI will try out for the heroine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Momo-chan, you just want to meet him, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a fan too, so I guess I'll cheer him on.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's all three try out together.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho-chan too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,S—Sure—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time, so if you'd please get ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this a success.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.43,0:19:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.99,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta do our best for all of our fans!
