Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's all boys!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.78,0:20:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you all waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's about to start.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.12,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please welcome the "St. Viz Girls" choir.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Underclassmen!!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,G—Good afternoon everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.76,0:20:17.13,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for joining us here today.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho sure is nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.57,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Miho-chan, just relax.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.54,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Shall we get started?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee, good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.15,0:20:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,P—Please enjoy the show.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.44,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is "The Daybreak Symphony."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:48.00,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say it or will you hold back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:54.52,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Please don't hide all the feelings deep in your heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It hits you even harder when you listen to it live.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.69,0:20:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Onee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:58.03,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Let them all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.98,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,I'm lonely and I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:05.78,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,I'm so sad that I might break.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't watch anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't look away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:09.55,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,I want you to look only at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho's up there doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:13.58,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Into my heart, never wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:18.88,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,Your touch, your gaze, your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.13,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,My heart aches just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:24.34,InsertSong,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}What are you waiting for—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.59,0:21:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two. Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.85,0:21:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you take this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.78,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a "St. Viz Girls" event today in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I made her take this afterward.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say anything about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki told me not to say anything \Nabout it because she was embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already been on TV, so what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.91,0:21:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, you just don't \Nunderstand a woman's feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna be able to come up \Nwith a cute manga heroine that way.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.36,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, mind your own business.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miho really did great.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.75,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Her singing still isn't that great,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.34,0:22:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but when she was speaking, she did \Nher best to get the audience excited.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She spoke about ten times \Nmore than she usually does.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.76,0:22:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.90,0:22:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she used to always be so shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.06,0:22:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody there liked her.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.77,0:22:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.59,0:22:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.20,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.64,0:22:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell her I showed you that picture, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.54,0:22:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll get mad at me.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.78,0:22:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always doing stuff like this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:30.11,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H4E4545&\frz0\blur1.003\fs70.194\move(766.667,43.454,766.667,-277.435)}Azuki Miho
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:30.11,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H5B5152&\frz0\blur1.003\fs70.194\move(633.333,147.074,633.333,-173.815)}It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:30.11,Cellphone,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H696161&\frz0\fscx90\blur1.003\fs48.133\move(213.333,748.741,213.333,427.852)}I heard about the Koogy thing. Don't worry, I'm sure \Nthat you guys will get first in the "Golden Future Cup."\NFIGHT!!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.18,0:22:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she believes we can get \Nfirst in the "Golden Future Cup."
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.38,0:22:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.00,0:22:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rewrite the name after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered "Why am I the only one having a hard time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:55.27,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,doushite boku dake ga kon'nani tsurai no ka to itsumo omotteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The people around me all seemed so happy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:00.73,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mawari no hito bakari shiawase sou ni mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But when I talked to you, I felt just a little bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:08.24,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,dakedo kimi to hanashitara sukoshi dakedakedo ki ga raku ni natta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because we were open with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:13.74,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,nita youna koto uchiakete kuretakara kana
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the reality you can't see with your eyes is like a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:21.25,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kao no mienai genjitsu ga toki ni kaibutsu no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our ambitions are crushed, but we move on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:28.51,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,bokura no kokorozashi wo tsubusou to oshiyosete kurukeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can say from the bottom of my heart that I'm glad I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.51,0:23:34.64,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,deaete yokatta to kokoro kara ieru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,People are multiplying little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.56,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hito ga sukoshi zutsu fuete ku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,While clenching their warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.31,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sono nukumori wo kamishimenagara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could support each other or face the boring things head on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:47.28,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,sasae attari hikutsu wo butsuke attari
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll finally arrive at that place alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:50.49,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hitori ja tadori tsukenai basho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}We're now proceeding en route
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:57.33,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}bokura wa ima kitto omomuite iru tochuu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:06.42,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}en route
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:06.42,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}tochuu
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.97,0:24:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, are you serious about rewriting the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:19.81,Next Ep,,0,0,0,,{\pos(80,76.88)\blur0.334\clip(53,78,1168,230)}Next\NEpisode
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Do you have time for that?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.52,0:24:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't do that, we \Nwon't be able to beat the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.50,0:24:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then I'll be cheering you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.39,0:24:29.99,Next Ep,,0,0,0,,{\pos(118.667,40.111)\blur0.334\clip(83,40,452,186)}Tuesday and \NFriday
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.75,0:24:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: Tuesday and Friday.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.56,0:24:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's dreams are coming together at last!
